  Text: |-
    Connected Lenses: Sync Controls
    
    This Lens demonstrates how values can be synchronized across a Connected Lenses session in real time.
    
    Use the UIKit example control panels to adjust the available settings. As you change a value, it instantly updates for all participants in the session — allowing everyone to see the changes reflected live within the Lens.
    
    Experience seamless, shared interaction across users.
